  <p>Sets the pipeline's emissive color, in the standard OpenGL lighting
model. It will look like the surface is a light source emitting this
color.</p>  <p>The default value is (0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0)</p>
  <p>Since 2.0</p>
